<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Frantic" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Frantic,</orth> mad: <cit><quote>f. with grief,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 762" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 762</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he is f. too,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.116" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 4, 116</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.29" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 1, 29</bibl>. <cit><quote>the lover, all as f., sees Helen's beauty in a brow of Egypt,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 10</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.185" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 3, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.89" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 3, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.247" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 247</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.68" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 68</bibl> (Qq <emph>tragic</emph>). <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.59" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.64" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 64</bibl>.
